{
  "stem": "26111.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The-- I, I became an expert in finding places to get away from the street and the, the stare and the examine of these bully types of the [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] custodians of the salute.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I, I didn't-- just once, I, I, I ran-- that one time I ran.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They, they-- I didn't get there in time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they started to come after me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I-- and I ran.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Phwt!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I ran into a side street.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they-- by the time I got to the end of the side street, they'd, they'd-- I, I think I could run faster.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They had boots on and all the other crap that they wear.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they couldn't get too far away from the-- from the corps.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They had, had other jobs to do, i.e., beat other people up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Remember that I went to England almost exactly one month-- or exactly one month after Kristallnacht, which was 10th of November.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went to-- I left on 10th of December.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So the main ones that I was aware of were the ones I've mentioned, summarized about doctors and lawyers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The ones about shops didn't date from that time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They, they dated from long before.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There were-- must have been many others which had been accumulating ever since the end of the Olympic Games.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "According to people that have studied the subject, there were-- there were many governing all aspects of daily life.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But they didn't affect us directly apart from this kind of business of the stormtroopers, and so on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But the regulations, per se, didn't affect us that I knew of.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Maybe my father knew about them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Maybe the-- my mother knew about them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I didn't know about them.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
